Maren Sanchez was stabbed to death in a hallway at Jonathan Law High School in Milford on April 25, 2014 . 
  Christopher Plaskon has been charged with murder as an adult over her death . 
  The 16-year-old was attacked after she turned down his offer to go to prom with her new boyfriend . 
  On Saturday hundreds of people gathered to remember Sanchez at a road race and music event . 
 